<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=George_Orwell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=33" title="Edit section: Poems">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Poems</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i>Romance</i></li>
<li><i>A Little Poem</i></li>
<li><i>Awake! Young Men of England</i></li>
<li><i>Kitchener</i></li>
<li><i>Our Minds are Married, But we are Too Young</i></li>
<li><i>The Lesser Evil</i></li>
<li><i>Poem from Burma</i></li>
<li><i>The Pagan</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoempagan.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoempagan.aspx" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li><i>Suggested By A Toothpaste Advertisement</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemtoothpaste.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemtoothpaste.aspx" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
<li><i>Summer-like For An Instant</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemsummerlike.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemsummerlike.aspx" rel="nofollow">[4]</a></li>
<li><i>A Dressed Man And A Naked Man</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemdressednaked.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemdressednaked.aspx" rel="nofollow">[5]</a></li>
<li><i>On A Ruined Farm Near The His Master’s Voice Gramophone Factor</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemhmv.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemhmv.aspx" rel="nofollow">[6]</a></li>
<li><i>A Happy Vicar I Might Have Been</i> <a href="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemhappyvicar.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.theorwellprize.co.uk/the-award/works/orwellpoemhappyvicar.aspx" rel="nofollow">[7]</a></li>
</ul>
